\h1\Input Recorder\h1\
\b\Record and play back keyboard and mouse input\b\
A small \b\GUI-application\b\ that makes it easy to \b\record\b\, \b\play back\b\ and share \b\keyboard and mouse\b\ input in shape of a \b\macro\b\.
Windows only.

\h2\Features\h2\
1. Record \b\mouse movement\b\ and \b\mouse buttons\b\
2. Record \b\keyboard input\b\
3. \b\Play back\b\ recorded macros
4. \b\Save and load\b\ recorded macros
5. \b\Restrict\b\ recorded macros to be playable \b\once only\b\